# Git Rules

## Branch Naming

- Pattern: (feature|bugfix|hotfix|chore)/{ticket}-{description}
- Example: feature/AI-123-add-new-endpoint

## Commit Messages

- Format: type(scope): description
- Types: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, test, chore
- Max length: 72 characters

## Hooks

- Required hooks:
  - pre-commit
  - pre-push
